				<td colspan="2"><span>Almost any class can duo pretty well with a bard.  Check the guides especially this one http://www.eqdiva.com/EQ/Guide.aspx?id=55&amp;ForumID=132
<br />

<br />
Depending on what you're hunting and where you're hunting it can be even better.  I recall hunting Walrus in EW with a Cleric and a Warrior.  I was twisting haste/slow/DS/bbb/Amp and pulling dark blues non stop.  The Cleric joined in meleeing and nuking as the Walrus were dying so fast and no one was needing to be healed.  Pretty sweet.  </span></td>
